videos.description: South Carolina's A'ja Wilson gets the steal and goes down court and finishes with the layup.
videos.headline: Wilson goes coast-to-coast with steal and score

videos.description: South Carolina's A'ja Wilson gets the offensive rebound and finishes with the layup to help pad the Gamecocks' lead in the first quarter.
videos.headline: Wilson gets the rebound and the bucket
